{
  "total_duration": 427.634,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 26.864,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你出去旅行，本来想好好玩。可脑子里一直飘着一个小任务：假期作业还没写、照片还没发、答应朋友的消息还没回。你每天都想一想，越想越烦。最后一天，你郑重其事地说：「我今天一定搞定。」然后忙了一整天——结果，真正完成的东西是零。60 年前，这个小任务叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "postcards"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，明信片。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 27.214,
      "end": 41.285,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "去年夏天，主角去了意大利。他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "visited museums"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，还坐在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "public gardens"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里晒太阳、看风景。表面看，这是一个特别舒服的假期。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 41.635,
      "end": 57.887,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "旅途中还有一位"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "friendly waiter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，教了他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a few words of Italian"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，又借给他一本书。主角读了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a few lines"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，但"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "did not understand a word"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——一点都没懂。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 58.236,
      "end": 73.708,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是他的脑子并没有完全在意大利。因为"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Postcards always spoil my holidays"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。明信片不是把假期砸坏了，而是像一条没回的消息，一直悬在心里，搅得人不安宁。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 74.058,
      "end": 94.162,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到最后一天，他终于"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "made a big decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。听起来很隆重，对吧？结果这个重大决定只是：早起去买了三十七张卡片。他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spent the whole day"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在房间里，可最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "did not write a single card"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——一张都没写。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 94.512,
      "end": 107.355,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先说一个老物件："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "postcard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，明信片。以前旅行时，人们会买一张风景卡，写几句话，寄给朋友，意思差不多是：「我到这里了，我想到你了，你看这张小照片。」"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 107.705,
      "end": 113.038,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "像现在发旅行照片、朋友圈、视频，或者给亲戚发一条消息？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 113.388,
      "end": 130.02,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。媒介变了，但那个感觉没变：你答应要分享、要回复、要写点什么，可你一边玩一边惦记它。课文第一句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Postcards always spoil my holidays."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是说明信片会物理摧毁假期。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 130.37,
      "end": 132.512,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是它把心情弄坏了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 132.862,
      "end": 146.334,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "没错。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spoil"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里就是「毁掉心情、搅乱兴致」。主角人在意大利，去了博物馆，坐了公园，还遇到友好的服务员。按理说假期很美。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 146.684,
      "end": 152.285,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但他每天都想明信片："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Everyday I thought about postcards."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 152.634,
      "end": 161.77,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，这就像假期作业、未读消息、没整理的旅行照片。最搞笑的是最后一天。他说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I made a big decision."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 162.12,
      "end": 164.677,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听起来像人生转折点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 165.027,
      "end": 176.059,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结果只是去买三十七张卡。更绝的是，他买完还"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spent the whole day in my room"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，动作很多、仪式感很足，可核心任务没碰。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 176.409,
      "end": 181.099,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以笑点不是懒，是「我看起来很努力，但其实还没开始」。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 181.449,
      "end": 203.769,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对！最后一句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I did not write a single card!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "特别有戏。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not a single"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "no"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更夸张，意思是「连一张都没有」。这就是拖延症的自我欺骗：准备了很多，完成了零。咱们听一遍原文，专门听这个越来越离谱的故事链。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 204.119,
      "end": 207.239,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Postcards always spoil my holidays."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 207.588,
      "end": 210.42,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last summer, I went to Italy."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 210.77,
      "end": 214.466,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I visited museums and sat in public gardens."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 214.816,
      "end": 218.392,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A friendly waiter taught me a few words of Italian."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 218.742,
      "end": 220.974,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then he lent me a book."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 221.324,
      "end": 225.14,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I read a few lines, but I did not understand a word."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 225.49,
      "end": 228.346,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Everyday I thought about postcards."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 228.696,
      "end": 233.208,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My holidays passed quickly, but I did not send cards to my friends."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 233.558,
      "end": 236.606,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "On the last day I made a big decision."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 236.955,
      "end": 240.243,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I got up early and bought thirty-seven cards."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 240.593,
      "end": 245.249,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I spent the whole day in my room, but I did not write a single card!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 245.599,
      "end": 248.311,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "spoil"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spoil"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 248.661,
      "end": 250.269,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "spoil"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spoil"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 250.619,
      "end": 273.691,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "spoil"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spoil"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以表示「弄坏、糟蹋」，但这一课不是说卡片把假期摔碎了。课文里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spoil my holidays"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是「毁掉我的好心情、让假期不得安宁」。比如你去海边玩，却一直想着没写完的作业，就可以说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The homework spoiled my holiday."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 274.04,
      "end": 276.816,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "decision"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 277.166,
      "end": 278.822,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "decision"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 279.172,
      "end": 301.371,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "decision"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是「决定」。动词是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "decide"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，名词是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，常用搭配是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "make a decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文里说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I made a big decision"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，听起来特别重大，但他只是决定去买明信片，所以这里有一点夸张的幽默感。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 301.721,
      "end": 304.497,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "single"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "single"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 304.847,
      "end": 306.479,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "single"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "single"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 306.829,
      "end": 325.884,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "single"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "single"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是「单个的、一个的」。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not a single card"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是普通的「没有卡片」，而是「连一张都没有」。这个短语很有力度：你也可以说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I did not write a single word"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——我连一个词都没写。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 326.234,
      "end": 366.969,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课的语法点很实用：过去时怎样把一个故事一步一步讲完。你听这串动作："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "went"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "visited"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "taught"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "lent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "read"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "thought"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "made"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "got up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bought"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "did not write"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它们都在报告已经发生完的事。讲故事的时候，过去时就像一串镜头：去了哪里，做了什么，最后结果怎样。先别急着背一大张不规则动词表，先把这条故事链听出来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 367.319,
      "end": 382.159,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好——把今天这个「假期里背着小任务」的感觉，放进你自己的生活。下面有三个现代场景：假期作业、发照片、写日记。你不用寄明信片，只要从 word bank 里选短语，把三个空都补上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 382.509,
      "end": 396.605,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老师有一次旅行回来前，手机里堆了好多照片，心里一直想「今晚整理」，结果"
